        "concepts_to_understand": "Stakeholder analysis, particularly using models like the power/interest grid, is a critical component of the Identify Stakeholders process. This helps in understanding and categorizing stakeholders based on their influence and engagement levels. For 'High Power, Low Interest' stakeholders, the strategy is to 'Keep Satisfied'. This involves ensuring their needs are met and they are not negatively impacted, thereby preventing them from using their power to obstruct the project. This proactive management helps maintain project momentum and reduces potential risks arising from powerful, yet uninvolved, parties.",
