        "option_d_result": "INCORRECT - Documenting identified stakeholders and their characteristics in a stakeholder register is the primary output of the Identify Stakeholders process. This register serves as a comprehensive record of all identified stakeholders, including their roles, influence, interests, and potential impact. This activity is fundamental to ensuring that stakeholder information is captured and available for future project management activities.",
