      "question_pmp": "A project manager takes over a troubled construction project. A new and critical stakeholder, a municipal regulator, has joined the project and has a number of concerns. The project manager needs to quickly understand the project's scope, history of changes, and existing agreements to address the stakeholder's concerns effectively. What is the MOST appropriate FIRST action to take?",
